Launch Game
  Select Player Type for Player 1 and Player 2 (P1 white,P2 black)
  Start Game Command
  Initializes board and pieces
  P1 goes first Turn
  P1 moves
  P1 turn ends P2 turn starts
  P2 moves
  P2 turn ends and repeat

  Every Move
  only allow correct moves 
  check for repeat / looping moves = draw
  check for checks and check mates
